snippet.title: [Sneak out for some nice treats!] Fia's Night Out [No Commentary]
snippet.description:
Game link https://arcadekitten.itch.io/fias-night-out
Commentary: https://youtu.be/4x5C8LEsUZ8

Fia's Night Out is a short RPG maker game (with a bit of horror) by arcadekitten (which I already seen some of their games as from other let's players, and so I now play one of theirs for the first time), where you play as Fia, as she sneaks out to her mother and go outside, to get some nice treats, and some random tomato artist. This has all endings.

Overall, this game is good. Characters are cute, even the uncle. It's a straightforward game about getting some treats.. what you expect me to say something else about this?.. I'm sorry if there's nothing else to say.

Anyway, I hope you enjoy!
